<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[a3]</itype><trans> for women to be married (humorous). </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Mahálin dáyun íyang anak,</i><trans> He’ll have no trouble finding a husband for his daughter. </trans></eg>
