<sense n=""4""><number>4</number> <corr sic=""[""/><form id=""handuxmi"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""handúmi"" type=""lemma"">-i</abbr></form><trans><corr sic=""]""/> think on it, consider! </trans>
