<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""0""> <itype>[AN]</itype><trans> </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> comb the hair. </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> be a man (be one who combs his hair flat) (humorous). </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Bulagi siya. Maáyu mag siya ray naghinápay<corr sic=""."">,</corr></i><trans> Leave him. He’s not the only fish in the sea (lit. the only one who combs his hair flat).
