</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> new model. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Bag-ung háung kutsi,</i><trans> The newest model car. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Bag-ung háung hirdu,</i><trans> The latest style of hairdo.
