<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[B16; a12]</itype><trans> get an embarrassed expression on the face. </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""4""><number>4</number> <itype>[B1256]</itype><trans> be unripe, green. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ug mahilaw ang mangga ayawg ipakáun sa bátà,</i><trans> If the mango is green, don’t give it to the child to eat. </trans></eg>
