<sense n=""4""><number>4</number> <itype>[A; a12]</itype><trans> drive s.o. into working faster. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ayaw kug huráwa kay magkasáyup hinúun,</i><trans> Don’t hurry me because I’ll only botch it up. </trans></eg>
